            <p><strong>Gender:</strong> <span id="ViewStudent_Gender"></span></p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <span id="ViewStudent_Email"></span></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <span id="ViewStudent_Phone"></span></p>
